<br>
What's better for a ranger's offhand at level 52?<br>
<br>
jagged blade of mourning (13/25), or lamentation (9/19)<br>
<br>
offhand, so no dmg bonus.<br>
<br>
Using the above formula calculation, I get 9.47 for the lammy but 0.104 for the jagged blade?  Is there something wrong with the formula that it should be 10.4 instead?<br>
