Best taunters: hategiver, carnage, bloodfrenzy (ie. luclin v.high-end ++hate &quot;wish weapons&quot;), willsapper, wavecrasher, etc..  Anything that procs a slow spell is particularly nice.  Snare is pretty good, too, but not as good as slow.  If you're not high enough level to consider these kinds of weapons, aim for fast weapons.  Fast weapons of a similar ratio both out damage and out-taunt slow weapons.<br>
